---

<section class="relative py-20 sm:py-28 px-6 bg-screen">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="reveal">
      <h2 class="font-display text-5xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl text-green phosphor mb-8">
        GREETINGS, PROGRAM.
      </h2>

      <p class="font-body text-lg text-text-dim mb-12 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        MCP is open source and welcomes contributions. Whether you're fixing bugs, adding features, or improving docs — we want your help.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 glass-panel inline-block px-6 py-4 mb-8">
      <code class="font-mono text-sm text-green">
        <span class="text-green-dim">$</span> git clone https://github.com/mastercontrol/mcp.git
      </code>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
      <div class="font-mono text-sm text-text-dim space-y-2 max-w-md mx-auto text-left">
        <p>&gt; Fork the repository</p>
        <p>&gt; Create a feature branch</p>
        <p>&gt; Write tests for your changes</p>
        <p>&gt; Submit a pull request</p>
        <p>&gt; <span class="text-green">END OF LINE</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
